{"tid":1672260,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家十點唔好再鄭嘉穎式咆哮","createTime":"2019-10-24T04:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T14:15:47.000Z","uid":304769,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"15a59f3a08030959ce0fe809cb58d926b477ed00","tid":1672260,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:04:31.000Z","msg":"本人十分贊成窗邊咆哮，但係各位唔好再就咁鄭嘉穎式咆哮啦。尋晚聽到有絲打嗌到聲都沙埋，聽到都心痛。我建議大家都係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">買返個大聲公或者咪</span></strong></span></strong>，再唔係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">下載個手機大聲公app</span></span></strong>都好呀，例如apple store 有個megaphone app。<br />\n<br />\n大家嗌都要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">保護好自己聲帶</span></span></strong>啊<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一日未實現五大訴求，一日都要嗌</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n大家<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">幫手推</span></strong>，我要手足煲底相認既時候唔好聲帶有事"},{"pid":"758ca6223e45c6b4450208a949d920dce126abcf","tid":1672260,"uid":155674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zjAb4Yn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzjAb4Yn.jpg&h=80bcd2fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90eb88c7d3f4f49a7335000a8af9f11ae7a774be","tid":1672260,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:06:26.000Z","msg":"期待每晚十點聽到大家的聲音"},{"pid":"bb5de549ec4e90c600a41e4f63a00e64265454e4","tid":1672260,"uid":270307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:12:12.000Z","msg":"推有用post"},{"pid":"0c55ad56567b4372e7082ad0f50ebc2ebfbd514c","tid":1672260,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:12:25.000Z","msg":"好耐之前已經聽到有個長氣絲打買左大聲公<br />\n琴晚聽到有3-4個大聲公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":